p: \bSorry but I've been ordered to keep anyone from entering the Battle Pyramid for the time being.\nSomething about there being an insect infestation inside, I think.
\bSome guy wearing a Team Rocket outfit came by earlier, laughing like a madman as he shouted something about how he'd get rid of all the bugs inside even if he
had to rebuild the whole facility from scratch.
\bYou might think I'm crazy but I think we can trust that guy to get the job done.\nNot immediately, of course but probably a few months down the road.
\bI'm sure you'll love it when it's finished!
\bI'll trade you my Delta Plusle for a Minun, if you have one!
\bWell, come back if you change your mind!

\bWell, come back if you change your mind!
\bSo many crazy things to do here...
\bThe Battle Tower, the Battle Pyramid, the Tube Challenge...
\bI hope to try them all! I'm going to be the strongest trainer ever!
\bIf you're brave enough, I recommend taking on the Challenge Championship.
\bA lot of people call it the final challenge for any trainer- the toughest opponents from all over the world!
\bOne of my cousins came to the Battle Frontier to help test out the Tube Challenge.
\bWow, what a tough test- so many trainers in a row.
\bI hear there's a fantastic reward if you can make it all the way through, though.
\rHey, tell you what, why don't you take this? You'll need it for the tough challenges here.
\bYou know, they say the Battle Arena is tough, but I think it's just confusing.
\bNobody actually understands the rules- thats how they keep losing!
\bOho, I got to have a go at the Battle Pyramid today.
\bWhat fun! I got to meet several youngsters that I know are doing great things all over the world.
\bGym Leaders, Elite Four members... what an experience!
\bI just know the future is in good hands.
\bI don't have as much money as the guy over there.
\rYou'll have to do the Challenge Championship before you get into the Tube Challenge.
\rYou probably have to win at least once- but I'd recommend winning as much as you can!
\rI'm sure the rewards get better and better!
\bI found this really beautiful leaf last winter. Would you like to take a look at it?
\bWonderful! I hope you like the look of it.
\bHere, I'll even put it in your Delta Snorlax Book of Leaves for ya.
\bI hope you think that leaf is as pretty as I thought it!
The Zygarde Cell was sucked into the Zygarde Cube!
